unit.class: public class TickLabelEntity extends ChartEntity implements Cloneable, Serializable { /** For serialization. */ private static final long serialVersionUID = 681583956588092095L ; /** * Creates a new entity. * * @param area the area (null not permitted). * @param toolTipText the tool tip text (null permitted). * @param urlText the URL text for HTML image maps (null * permitted). */ public TickLabelEntity ( Shape area , String toolTipText , String urlText ) { super ( area , toolTipText , urlText ) ; } }
